class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n15度以下要著校褸，寒冷天氣先俾著街褸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n噉我件校褸得嗰好少日子要著仲買嚟做乜？<br />\n但唔買嗰啲喺15度同12度之間嘅日子又冇得唔著<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n講到階級觀念 <br />\n咁要限制埋用同一款既文具 同一款既書包啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n所以日本係用梗一樣嘅書包返學<br />\n<br />\n文具就算啦 中學生有幾多人會j文具<br />\n<br />\n所以講到底都係香港只學其形而不學其粹"},{"pid":"c4372b9808a2e422a5cb420331e697638c351070","tid":231354,"uid":12421,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-06T04:59:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>最撚on9仔 點解一定要著白襪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n著西褲著白襪 出到返工肯定比人笑到仆街啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n中學唔係純黑白灰都得嘅咩"},{"pid":"f77b536648af6b9d1992d6f3c456d07b70ead383","tid":231354,"uid":13149,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-06T05:03:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>最撚on9仔 點解一定要著白襪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n著西褲著白襪 出到返工肯定比人笑到仆街啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n中學唔係純黑白灰都得嘅咩</blockquote><br />\n我個間一定要白色<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 無論係著西褲定運動褲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"412103bfc3f5354158946d1aef8cf6f7c58df45b","tid":231354,"uid":4623,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-06T05:05:06.000Z","msg":"大陸中學生唔使著校服<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n覺得套校服設計好其實無咩問題<br />\n講到尾都係個人行為同選擇<br />\n決定個人特質同會唔會從眾<br />\n你掟個毒撚去邊佢都同你頺毒癈啦<br />\n我覺得就算你比學生自己選擇着唔着校服<br />\n佢哋都會自己着返因為呢個係一種身份認同<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7736d3d12251f4b0fb93371186fc310a32f21ce8","tid":231354,"uid":15935,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-06T05:06:29