quote><br />\n所以日本係用梗一樣嘅書包返學<br />\n<br />\n文具就算啦 中學生有幾多人會j文具<br />\n<br />\n所以講到底都係香港只學其形而不學其粹</blockquote><br />\n但小學生著便服返學架喎"},{"pid":"12ac9f660eb2da5dac4899de728c4fc30a5a5eff","tid":231354,"uid":46700,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-06T05:15:41.000Z","msg":"學校最初係訓練工人（唔知真定假）"},{"pid":"40ec29f9dad8abb6d198a9978201337c30e4d6e6","tid":231354,"uid":27718,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-06T05:15:55.000Z","msg":"男學生著校服做乜，女就唔同啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6769961fcb5405db51473520c5d330e377dccda8","tid":231354,"uid":34022,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-06T05:16:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>著校服幾好 日日諗著乜衫真係諗起都煩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n呢樣真<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n以前一放學到沖涼前都着住<br />\n瞓晏覺都照着"},{"pid":"f9c1ed661cc94886711914f9c0c1ded65746fb67","tid":231354,"uid":17232,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-06T05:17:52.000Z","msg":"咁撚多負皮？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n連登好撚低質"},{"pid":"ac8d920fea554e03effc6694dd07816bc9249042","tid":231354,"uid":54768,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-06T05:19:02.000Z","msg":"有讀過社會學應該唔陌生，<br />\n早會果陣叫你條隊排齊d，腳尖對住前面同學後踭，唔好亂郁。<br />\n仲有d濕鳩老師話我唔要聽到一粒聲，靜晒先准上課室。<br />\n依家諗返起根本反智，坐監都唔洗咁"},{"pid":"9ef5c63a0d8ed31a0c1ce2d8b5907c7e55a487c4","tid":231354,"uid":82532,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-06T05:21:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有讀過社會學應該唔陌生，<br />\n早會果陣叫你條隊排齊d，腳尖對住前面同學後踭，唔好亂郁。<br />\n仲有d濕鳩老師話我唔要聽到一粒聲，靜晒先准上課室。<br />\n依家諗返起根本反智，<span style=\"color: red;\">坐監都唔洗咁</span></blockquote><br />\n你肯定?"},{"pid":"5695cb33c89d862de3daa7d3c35b9094781e494e","tid":231354,"uid":38904,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime"